                     <interp inst="t18030112-13-person115" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            , a constable, produced the cards.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's defence. I bought the cards in Fenchurch-street. <rs id="t18030112-13-verdict70" type="verdictDescription">
